{"type": "article", "id": 22097, "title": "找回自己的“生物钟”｜火箭闹钟、Sleep Cycle", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3910, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">睡觉，可能是逃避糟糕情绪最简单的方法了。但说好要热爱工作的呢？还是先找回正常的作息时间吧。</p>\n<p class=\"\">朝九晚五的同学们可能需要一个粗暴的闹钟。不吵醒自己，誓不罢休。火箭闹钟( <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/huo-jian-nao-zhong/id705079162?mt=8\">iPhone </a>| <a href=\"http://www.wandoujia.com/apps/com.rocket.alarmclock\">Android</a> )里，还有 5 个难度不一的小游戏想要赶走你的瞌睡虫。还是起不来，绑定朋友的手机号码之后，他还能叫你起床。只是自愿承受起床气的朋友已经不多了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001919XbHRAyPm3BWuJ46n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">也有温和的办法。Sleep Cycle （<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/apple-store/id320606217?pt=63263&amp;ct=scsite&amp;mt=8\">iPhone</a>｜<a href=\"http://apps.wandoujia.com/apps/com.northcube.sleepcycle/download\">Andorid</a>）就尝试在浅睡眠状态中把你叫醒，减少“倒时差”的不适感。类似于妈妈边做早饭，边提醒你，“还有半小时就该起床了。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600191949UanRyzxmkTMQlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">为了提高检测睡眠状态的准确性，记得把手机插上电源后，放到枕头底下。</p>\n\n\n"}